snippet.title: Jason Momoa Reveals He Sues Amber Heard If Aquaman 2 FAILS!
snippet.description:
Jason Momoa Reveals He Sues Amber Heard If Aquaman 2 FAILS! 
Jason Momoa’s recent statements regarding the new Aquaman 2 movie have left fans stunned as Amber Heard has entered the spotlight. Due to Amber Heard’s involvement in a very popular legal battle against Johnny Heard, she has been all over the news. As the case begins to take turns that paint Amber in a controversial light, users and fans are increasingly concerned about her maintaining her role in the new movie. This is leading to huge boycott calls, reaching millions of signatures on the internet. The concern is genuine: is Amber Heard going to cause a massive failure of the Aquaman 2 movie? And if so, how is Jason Mamoa going to respond with his income at stake?
